race.comment: EXTREME TENSION (2) filled the minor money three on end before breaking through for a deserved win last time, scoring at this track over 520m (29.63). Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. DRINK TINS (7) could manage only second at this track last time but turned heads when posting a powerful 25.22 over 457m at Q Lakeside the start prior. Expecting another bold showing. DISTANCE DRUMS (3) goes very well here including two wins. Comes off a (29.77) win last time, scoring by 1.3 lengths in a Grade 5 over 520m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. TAGOVAILOA (1) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.
